### Test Product Seller Validation Endpoint
### These tests verify the validate-seller endpoint functionality

### Test 1: Validate seller for valid product and seller
GET http://localhost:5003/api/products/{{productId}}/validate-seller/{{sellerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Variables for testing
# @productId = existing product ID (replace with actual)
# @sellerId = existing seller ID (replace with actual)

### Test 2: Validate seller for non-existent product
GET http://localhost:5003/api/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/validate-seller/{{sellerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 3: Validate seller for product with different seller
GET http://localhost:5003/api/products/{{productId}}/validate-seller/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 4: Test with invalid GUIDs (should return BadRequest)
GET http://localhost:5003/api/products/invalid-guid/validate-seller/another-invalid-guid
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Expected responses:
# Test 1: 200 OK with IsValid: true, Product details
# Test 2: 200 OK with IsValid: false, Error: "Product not found"
# Test 3: 200 OK with IsValid: false, Error: "Product does not belong to the specified seller"
# Test 4: 400 BadRequest for invalid GUID format
